title: WGA Diag Tool -Remove Nags  Windows Validation
description:
Sick of the Nagging? Have a pirated version of Windows?

Microsoft is becoming more advanced in their attack on pirated versions of Windows XP or Microsoft Office. 

The newest patches produce popups on the login screen and on the desktop explaining that this version of Windows is not genuine and the owner may be the victim of software counterfeiting. 

Now you can remove all that garbage with one easy tool and authenticate windows for good.

Enjoy!
